        public static NAryTreeNode copyTree(NAryTreeNode root)
        given a root node, copy the tree and return it. The attributes of NAryTreeNode copied are data, parent and children. The next and prev attributes are not copied currently, but could be added upon need. The runtime complexity is O(|V|).
